<div class="toplang">
<p><span>Available Languages: </span><a href="./en/dns-caveats.html" title="English">&nbsp;en&nbsp;</a> |
<a href="./fr/dns-caveats.html" hreflang="fr" rel="alternate" title="Français">&nbsp;fr&nbsp;</a> |
